{"_id":"03817db9bd564271","name":"Acid Bomb","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]D","force":1,"description":"<p>This area-effect spell strikes targets with a spray of acid,using the elemental effect rules (Elemental Effects, p. 112).</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!03817db9bd564271"}
{"_id":"0fd5e75703ab4b31","name":"Acid Stream","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]D","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell strikes the target with a stream of acid, using the elemental effect rules (Elemental Effects, p. 112).</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!0fd5e75703ab4b31"}
{"_id":"d75d7517855f43eb","name":"Acid","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]S","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell strikes the target with a spray of acid, using the elemental effect rules. (See Elemental Effects, p. 112.).</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!d75d7517855f43eb"}
{"_id":"4b27689405f44da3","name":"Agonizing Pain","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]M","force":1,"description":"<p>The agonizing pain spell inflicts temporary Stun damage on a target equal to the caster's successes. With 10 or more successes, it incapacitates the subject. The subject suffers no actual damage and the pain can be resisted with a successful Willpower Test.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!4b27689405f44da3"}
{"_id":"f434fcb7c5f14999","name":"Air Breathing","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]L","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!f434fcb7c5f14999"}
{"_id":"c3eab5fd43f649d7","name":"Allergy","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]S","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!c3eab5fd43f649d7"}
{"_id":"9340373bef184091","name":"Alleviate Mild Allergy","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)M","force":1,"description":"<p>The alleviate allergy spell allows the spellcaster to reduce the effects of an allergy suffered by the spell's target. For example, an alleviate severe allergy spell would protect a vampire exposed to sunlight. Because it does not aid against vulnerabilities, however, the alleviate allergy spell would not protect the vampire from an attack with a wooden weapon.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!9340373bef184091"}
{"_id":"1dbed3d9f1544d04","name":"Alleviate Moderate Allergy","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)S","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!1dbed3d9f1544d04"}
{"_id":"ae5f488344824436","name":"Alleviate Nuissance Allergy","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)L","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!ae5f488344824436"}
{"_id":"d2632006e16e4b2e","name":"Alleviate Severe Allergy","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)D","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!d2632006e16e4b2e"}
{"_id":"54c9d254473041c2","name":"Alter Temperature","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]S","force":1,"description":"<p>This area-effect spell changes the ambient temperature by 5 degrees Celsius for every 2 successes. Extreme temperatures can cause damage to those without protection.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!54c9d254473041c2"}
{"_id":"8051001b262e439d","name":"Analyze Device","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"detection","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]M","force":1,"description":"<p>A specific hypersense spell requiring a voluntary subject. The magician can analyze the purpose and basic operation of a device or piece of equipment. The magician's previous familiarity with the device or similar objects reduces the target number by -2. The base target number for this spell is based on the object's resistance, see p. 130.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!8051001b262e439d"}
{"_id":"6f8b06e9c1b343db","name":"Analyze Magic","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"detection","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)M","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell allows the casting magician to analyze a magic item as if assensing it. To determine the effect of the spell, make the Spell Force test using the Force Rating of the spell, focus, or other magical phenomena as the target number. To determine the information the caster acquires,consult the Astral Examination table (p. 146, SRII).</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!6f8b06e9c1b343db"}
{"_id":"74bf636c2acb4621","name":"Analyze Truth","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"detection","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)S","force":1,"description":"<p>A hypersense spell. The magician can tell whether a target's statement is the truth or not. The target makes a Spell Resistance Test using his Willpower Rating against the Force of the spell to reduce the spellcaster's successes. The caster needs at least 1 success to determine validity. The spell does not work on written materials. The magician must hear a statement to know if it is true or not.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!74bf636c2acb4621"}
{"_id":"ae0ecf03cd2e4479","name":"Animal Spy","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"detection","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)L","force":1,"description":"<p>The animal spy spell enables a magician to perceive his surroundings using the senses of any non-paranormal animal. The animal must be within a range of meters in a circle around the caster determined by the following formula: Spell Test Successes x Magic Attribute × 5. The spellcaster has no control over the animal's actions and cannot target spells using the animal's eyesight. As long as the magician sustains the spell, he can switch to the senses of any other animal within the spell's range by spending a Simple Action. If the gamemaster believes that a targeted animal would have some reason to resist this spell (most animals would be completely unaware of it), he may make a Willpower Test against the Force of the spell. If the test succeeds, the spell does not affect the animal.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!ae0ecf03cd2e4479"}
{"_id":"8beb9018b6cf490e","name":"Animate","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell allows the caster to make inanimate objects move. The object moves according to its structure (balls can roll, rugs may crawl, humanoid statues can walk, and so on.). The spell imparts a certain amount of flexibility, allowing solid things like statues to move as if they had joints. The caster can only move the whole object, not just one part of it such as computer keys or vehicle weapons. Movement continues for a number of meters per action equal to one-half the caster's Magic Attribute Rating (round down).</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!8beb9018b6cf490e"}
{"_id":"912b7774da88412a","name":"Antidote D Toxin","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"permanent","drain_code":"(F/2)D","force":1,"description":"<p>These curative spells act on a toxin (poison or drug) or the disease, not the person affected by them. The Spell Success Test has a target number equal to the Strength (Power) of the infection or toxin. The antidote spell must be used before the toxin damages the victim. Its successes directly reduce the Strength of the toxin at a one-to-one ratio, making it easier for the target to make his own Resistance Tests.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!912b7774da88412a"}
{"_id":"62856b3036864f39","name":"Antidote L Toxin","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"permanent","drain_code":"(F/2)L","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!62856b3036864f39"}
{"_id":"6b11cbc443334c5e","name":"Antidote M Toxin","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"permanent","drain_code":"(F/2)M","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!6b11cbc443334c5e"}
{"_id":"660f30d9c88243c5","name":"Antidote S Toxin","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"permanent","drain_code":"(F/2)S","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!660f30d9c88243c5"}
{"_id":"e7a8b779ebe34d8e","name":"Armor","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>A voluntary subject is required. The magician gives the subject built-in armor, knitting his tissues into tougher compounds. Treat one-half the successes made in the Spell Success Test as the Dermal Armor Rating (add to Body) for as long as the spell is maintained.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!e7a8b779ebe34d8e"}
{"_id":"f1e75534f7be4e38","name":"Arrow Barrier","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!f1e75534f7be4e38"}
{"_id":"2738d1afbdda4ab0","name":"Astral Perception","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"detection","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)S","force":1,"description":"<p>Detection spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!2738d1afbdda4ab0"}
{"_id":"b8418cacc0324e27","name":"Astral Sense","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"detection","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)M","force":1,"description":"<p>The astral sense spell enables the spellcaster to sense the presence of astrally active forms within the spell's range (spellcaster's Magic Attribute × 5 meters), even if the character is not astrally active at the time. To use the spell, the magician makes a Spell Success (10) Test. All standard modifiers apply to this test. Each success on the Spell Success Test allows the character to sense astrally active forms of a Force or Magic rating equal to the number of successes. For example, 3 successes allow a character to sense all the items of Force or Magic Rating 3 or below within range, but not a Rating 5 ward. This spell cannot differentiate between spirits, spells and other astrally active forms such as foci and wards.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!b8418cacc0324e27"}
{"_id":"03560e97721c4612","name":"Astral Static","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]D","force":1,"description":"<p>This area-effect spell creates a cloud of crackling,swirling mana in astral space, generating a background count of I for every 2 successes the caster rolls. As with normal background count (see Background Count, p. 89) the rating of the static increases the target numbers of all AstralSuccess Tests within the area of effect, including the caster's target numbers.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!03560e97721c4612"}
{"_id":"7fe73350583846f1","name":"Aural Entertainment","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]L","force":1,"description":"<p>Illusion spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!7fe73350583846f1"}
{"_id":"746376d0d4d04ff8","name":"Awaken","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)-1]L","force":1,"description":"<p>The awaken spell instantly wakes the target. It can also revive unconscious subjects, but they'll only stay awake for one minute per success before falling unconscious again.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!746376d0d4d04ff8"}
{"_id":"985609e084a5452e","name":"Barrier","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]S","force":1,"description":"<p>Barrier is an area-effect spell in which the magician forms a force field of crackling energy. The Spell Success Test has a Target Number 6. The magician may form the barrier as a normal area spell, which would create a dome of energy, or he may create a wall. The wall's height is the spell's Force in meters. The length of the wall or radius of the dome is equal to the magician's Magic Rating. This length may be adjusted in the same way as the radius of an area effect, by withholding dice from the Success Test. The magician may make the wall into any shape. Anything the size of a molecule (or less) can pass the barrier, including air or other gases. Anything bigger treats a physical barrier as having a Barrier Rating equal to the spell's Force (and is therefore cumulative with armor). Attacks directed through a barrier spell have a visibility modifier of -1. Physical barriers do not impede spells, even manipulation spells.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!985609e084a5452e"}
{"_id":"fdefad41248f4af5","name":"Bind","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]S","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell entraps and holds the target in bands of mystical energy. The magician makes a Spell Success Test using the target's Quickness Attribute Rating as the target number. The target resists by making a Quickness SuccessTest against a target number equal to the Force Rating of the spell. Net successes in the caster's favor provide the effectiveBarrier Rating of the mystic energy. The character can attempt to escape by breaking the bands. In this situation, compare the character's StrengthRating to the Barrier Rating, per those rules (p. 98, SRII). The character must make a Strength Success Test against a target number equal to the Force Rating of the spell in order to exert more pressure against the bonds. Every 2 successes the character rolls allows him to increase his effectiveStrength Rating by 1 for this purpose. Upon breaking free, he must make a Body Success Test to resist (Character'sStrength)L Stun damage, representing the fatigue caused by his efforts.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!fdefad41248f4af5"}
{"_id":"50617ffa259c42ee","name":"Biophysical Armor","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!50617ffa259c42ee"}
{"_id":"444b85b0cba041b5","name":"Black Wall","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Illusion spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!444b85b0cba041b5"}
{"_id":"4d6f961e20444801","name":"Blackout","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Illusion spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!4d6f961e20444801"}
{"_id":"3efbb77b72944380","name":"Blade Barrier","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Similar to the physical barrier spell (p. 158, SRII) and the bullet barrier spell following, this spell provides protection against bladed weapons. The barrier's effective BarrierRating equals the spell's Force Rating. The Impact ArmorRating may be added to the Barrier Rating. The personal form of this spell has a Drain Code of [(F / 2)+2]L.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!3efbb77b72944380"}
{"_id":"cdab685a34614ad2","name":"Blast Barrier","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Similar to the physical barrier spell (p. 158, SRII), this spell provides protection against blast from grenades and similar weapons. The barrier's effective Barrier Ratingequals the spell's Force Rating. The Impact Armor Ratingmay be added to the Barrier Rating. The personal form of this spell has a Drain Code of [(F / 2)+2]L.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!cdab685a34614ad2"}
{"_id":"d28265331b4645fb","name":"Blindness","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]D","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell magically blinds a subject for its duration by affecting the brain's ability to process visual information. It works on subjects with cybereyes as well as natural eyes.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!d28265331b4645fb"}
{"_id":"29a3234d226f43cd","name":"Blunder","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)D","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!29a3234d226f43cd"}
{"_id":"d7fe075feaa74be5","name":"Bug Barrier","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]D","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!d7fe075feaa74be5"}
{"_id":"f44f87b13a7e403c","name":"Bullet Barrier","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Similar to the physical barrier spell (p. 158, SRII), the bullet barrier spell provides protection against bullets and other ballistic weapons. The barrier's effective Barrier Rating equals the spell's Force Rating. The Ballistic Armor Rating can be added to the Barrier Rating. The personal form of this spell has a Drain Code of [(F / 2)+2]L.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!f44f87b13a7e403c"}
{"_id":"4f9ffb5df99f4026","name":"Buzz","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"permanent","drain_code":"(F/2)S","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!4f9ffb5df99f4026"}
{"_id":"f9b14aced6bd49d3","name":"Calm Animal","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]L","force":1,"description":"<p>The calm animal spell makes a subject with animal-level intelligence calm and passive. Subjects in combat have a reduced target number to resist.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!f9b14aced6bd49d3"}
{"_id":"227534e5848a49f4","name":"Camouflage","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]L","force":1,"description":"<p>Illusion spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!227534e5848a49f4"}
{"_id":"c0e7d64fd63e422d","name":"Catalogue","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"detection","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)-1]L","force":1,"description":"<p>The catalogue spell is a simple area-effect spell that enables the spellcaster to compile a comprehensive, itemized list of all of the non living items within his line of sight. If the Spell Test succeeds, the caster becomes able to write or dictate a list of all the items in a manner similar to automatic writing. (If the spell's area of effect contains items that the magician would not recognize on sight, they will be listed as \"unknown.\") The spell cannot catalogue what the spellcaster cannot see. A warehouse full of boxes, for example, will list the number of boxes rather than what the boxes contain. As soon as he produces the list, the caster forgets the exact items and quantities.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!c0e7d64fd63e422d"}
{"_id":"251509cdbfc04a12","name":"Catfall","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]L","force":1,"description":"<p>The catfall spell psychokinetically slows a target's fall and ensures an upright landing. The distance it cushions is determined by the caster's successes and Magic Attribute.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!251509cdbfc04a12"}
{"_id":"a9ca9515e41e4dbb","name":"Cause Mild Allergy","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!a9ca9515e41e4dbb"}
{"_id":"9e1bc530b2c84797","name":"Cause Moderate Allergy","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]S","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!9e1bc530b2c84797"}
{"_id":"8c9cf0de62494137","name":"Cause Nuissance Allergy","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]L","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!8c9cf0de62494137"}
{"_id":"f49291dbede8435d","name":"Cause Severe Allergy","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]D","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!f49291dbede8435d"}
{"_id":"e839527a12144334","name":"Chaff","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)-1]S","force":1,"description":"<p>A variation of chaotic world, this spell adds +1 to the target numbers for all non-living sensing devices, including smartgun links.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!e839527a12144334"}
{"_id":"920995fcc7544d7d","name":"Chained Lightning","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+3]D","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!920995fcc7544d7d"}
{"_id":"34bc8f4ee37b4df2","name":"Chaos","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>A target who fails to resist a chaos spell is subject to massive distractions. The spell consumes all senses in a cloud of blinding sights, fierce odors, and tickling sensations. A major distraction (+1 to all target numbers) is suffered for every extra success the spell has after being reduced by the Spell Resistance Test. This spell can also deceive technological sensing devices in addition to the target's own senses.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!34bc8f4ee37b4df2"}
{"_id":"ff22093fd75c46f0","name":"Chaotic World","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]S","force":1,"description":"<p>This is an area-effect version of the chaos spell.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!ff22093fd75c46f0"}
{"_id":"9bb55926633747ab","name":"Clair Spell (Extended)","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"detection","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]S","force":1,"description":"<p>Detection spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!9bb55926633747ab"}
{"_id":"de9d04790a8c449b","name":"Clair Spell","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"detection","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Detection spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!de9d04790a8c449b"}
{"_id":"6a3aef2a4c8f4007","name":"Clairaudience (Extended)","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"detection","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)-1]S","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell works in a manner similar to the clairaudience spell (p. 153, SRII), but includes the Extended Range option. For a complete explanation of Extended Range, see SpellDesign, p.110.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!6a3aef2a4c8f4007"}
{"_id":"3b56ba1651964a29","name":"Clairaudience","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"detection","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)M","force":1,"description":"<p>A hypersense spell. The magician can hear distant sounds as if present, to the range of the new sense. The magician must concentrate to use this sense, and while using it, cannot use physical hearing. This spell does not translate visual images.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!3b56ba1651964a29"}
{"_id":"18a65a61a9234b62","name":"Clairvoyance (Extended)","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"detection","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)-1]S","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell works in a manner similar to the clairvoyance spell (p. 153, SRII), but includes the Extended Range option.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!18a65a61a9234b62"}
{"_id":"30b3a501008b4157","name":"Clairvoyance","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"detection","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)M","force":1,"description":"<p>A hypersense spell requiring a voluntary subject. The magician can see distant scenes as if present, to the range of the new sense. The magician must concentrate to use this sense, and while using it, cannot use physical vision. A magician cannot cast spells at a target seen using the clairvoyance spell. This spell does not translate sound.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!30b3a501008b4157"}
{"_id":"db2b8bfdc3774104","name":"Clean Air","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]S","force":1,"description":"<p>This area-effect spell removes impurities from the air. The target number for the spell depends on the level of impurities.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!db2b8bfdc3774104"}
{"_id":"9ad479612ded493e","name":"Clean Water","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"permanent","drain_code":"(F/2)S","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell purifies a volume of water in the spell's area of effect. The target number depends on the type of impurities.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!9ad479612ded493e"}
{"_id":"c87ef74b6dc940b6","name":"Clout","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)M","force":1,"description":"<p>This telekinetic punch carries a Damage Code of (Caster's Willpower)M Stun. Normal Ranged Combat modifiers apply(p. 87, SRII). Per the normal Ranged Combat rules,successes from the spell's casting may be used to increase the damage. Impact armor defends against this spell.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!c87ef74b6dc940b6"}
{"_id":"669fe88195cb422c","name":"Combat Sense","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"detection","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]S","force":1,"description":"<p>A hypersense spell requiring a voluntary subject. The subject becomes able to subconsciously analyze combat or other danger-ous situations. The theory is that the spell allows precognition, with the subject sensing events a split second before they occur. Every 2 successes adds to the subject's Combat Pool for the duration of the spell.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!669fe88195cb422c"}
{"_id":"ee1c0d09f0374189","name":"Compel Truth","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]L","force":1,"description":"<p>The compel truth spell forces a subject to speak what they believe to be the truth. The subject can choose not to speak but cannot deliberately lie.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!ee1c0d09f0374189"}
{"_id":"f89d2317849a48d3","name":"Confusion","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)S","force":1,"description":"<p>This is an area-effect spell similar to the chaos spell, except that the confusion spell does not affect technological systems. Visual illusions fill the affected area, making it a place of shifting forms, dazzling lights, and pools of shadow. Those who fail to resist suffer a distraction (+1 to all target numbers) for every two successes remaining after reductions from the Spell Resistance Test.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!f89d2317849a48d3"}
{"_id":"70c5cb3a90ac4eef","name":"Control Actions","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]S","force":1,"description":"<p>Like a puppeteer, the magician controls the physical actions of a target. The victim's consciousness is not affected, but becomes only a passenger in its own body. The victim uses any skills possessed at the magician's orders, but with +4 to all target numbers. The Threshold is the target's Willpower Rating.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!70c5cb3a90ac4eef"}
{"_id":"28bba177163d4144","name":"Control Animal","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]D","force":1,"description":"<p>Similar to the control thoughts spell (p. 157, SRII), this spell works only on non-sentient animals. Sentience is determined at the gamemaster's discretion. Paranormal animals should resist this spell with either Willpower orEssence, whichever is higher.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!28bba177163d4144"}
{"_id":"26f3ad57ce3f4546","name":"Control Emotion","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>The subject feels some overwhelming emotion, which can be anything the magician chooses when the spell is cast. The spell can make the target love somebody, hate somebody, or any other single emotion desired.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!26f3ad57ce3f4546"}
{"_id":"d8a3646400e34d9b","name":"Control Fire","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]S","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell allows a magician to control normal flames within their line of sight. The caster can move flames, make them flare, or contain them.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!d8a3646400e34d9b"}
{"_id":"6881dbd583a44323","name":"Control Thoughts","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]D","force":1,"description":"<p>The magician controls the thoughts of the subject. The victim will carry out orders wholeheartedly as long as the magician sustains the spell. This is the magical equivalent of deep hypnotic suggestion. Actions that would be terribly destructive to the target or his loved ones allow the character to fight the spell. He must pass a Willpower Test with a target number of the spell's Force. If the casting magician is not present, a single success will do. If the casting magician is present, roll that character's Willpower against a target number equal to the target's Willpower. The magician's successes reduce the target's. One net success on the part of the target is still all that is required to resist the heinous command.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!6881dbd583a44323"}
{"_id":"882e3b6299f3450d","name":"Corpse Cadavre","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"permanent","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]S","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!882e3b6299f3450d"}
{"_id":"bb744372d0c74092","name":"Cripple Limb","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)S","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell incapacitates a single organic limb upon a successful touch, rendering it useless for the spell's duration.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!bb744372d0c74092"}
{"_id":"8c5f381ec953443a","name":"(Critter) Form","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Similar to the shapechange spell listed later in this section, this spell allows the magician to change into a specific, non-paranormal animal. This spell requires a voluntary subject.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!8c5f381ec953443a"}
{"_id":"e8fd01b1546840d7","name":"Crowd Scene","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Illusion spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!e8fd01b1546840d7"}
{"_id":"c774901005104811","name":"Cure D Disease","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"permanent","drain_code":"(F/2)D","force":1,"description":"<p>The cure disease spell can be used at any point after infection, killing the germs in the patient's system and eliminating any symptoms at once, but it does not heal damage already done by the disease. That takes a separate healing spell. Successes from the cure spell directly reduce the Virulence (Power) of the disease at a one-to-one ratio, making the target's own Resistance Tests easier.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!c774901005104811"}
{"_id":"e0e5fe600bb04556","name":"Cure L Disease","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"permanent","drain_code":"(F/2)L","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!e0e5fe600bb04556"}
{"_id":"48d8ce4a349045fc","name":"Cure M Disease","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"permanent","drain_code":"(F/2)M","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!48d8ce4a349045fc"}
{"_id":"55c12bb36dfa4652","name":"Cure S Disease","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"permanent","drain_code":"(F/2)S","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!55c12bb36dfa4652"}
{"_id":"2696d668e74e478f","name":"Deafness","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!2696d668e74e478f"}
{"_id":"00db5f1cfe5c476d","name":"Death Touch","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"combat","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)-1]S","force":1,"description":"<p>A particularly lethal combat spell that requires the casting magician to touch the target. The spell causes Physical damage to a single target.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!00db5f1cfe5c476d"}
{"_id":"c329b238cb3e434b","name":"Decrease -1 Attribute","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]L","force":1,"description":"<p>The magician's Target Number is 10, minus the target's Essence. The target resists using the Attribute that is attacked, not necessarily his Body Rating. The success totals of both are com-pared. The magician needs only 1 success to affect the target. If an Attribute is reduced to 0, the target is helpless. If this is a Physical Attribute, the victim is unconscious or paralyzed. When a Mental Attribute is reduced to 0, the victim is standing about mindlessly.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!c329b238cb3e434b"}
{"_id":"60b799943192472f","name":"Decrease -1 Cybered Attribute","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+3]L","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell works in a manner similar to the decrease (Attribute) spell (p. 154, SRII) except that it affects cyberedAttributes. Increase the Drain Level by +1 for the version of this spell that affects cybered Reaction.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!60b799943192472f"}
{"_id":"0d5bbe43a17448e0","name":"Decrease -2 Attribute","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!0d5bbe43a17448e0"}
{"_id":"cf7346b616204aeb","name":"Decrease -2 Cybered Attribute","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+3]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!cf7346b616204aeb"}
{"_id":"b48eb1f54feb4a1e","name":"Decrease -3 Attribute","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]S","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!b48eb1f54feb4a1e"}
