{"_id":"1b5399bb15504bb3","name":"Decrease -4 Attribute","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]D","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!1b5399bb15504bb3"}
{"_id":"870e9bdf90d342e0","name":"Decrease -4 Cybered Attribute","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+3]D","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!870e9bdf90d342e0"}
{"_id":"e3c32b8a7fdb45d2","name":"Decrease Reflexes -1 die","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]S","force":1,"description":"<p>Similar to the increase reflexes spell (p. 155, SRII) this spell reduces the number of Initiative dice available to the target by the number indicated (-1, -2, or-3). This spell will not affect characters with cybernetic Initiative enhancements. Any character who ends up with no, or a negative number of Initiative dice as a result of this spell uses his or her Reaction as Initiative.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!e3c32b8a7fdb45d2"}
{"_id":"011561972ecd4c27","name":"Decrease Reflexes -2 dice","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]D","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!011561972ecd4c27"}
{"_id":"58e5c85306864571","name":"Decrease Reflexes -3 dice","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+3]D","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!58e5c85306864571"}
{"_id":"2b34a3d2d5444650","name":"Deflect","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]S","force":1,"description":"<p>The deflect spell psychokinetically deflects physical missile attacks. It provides extra dice for Damage Resistance Tests against ranged attacks.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!2b34a3d2d5444650"}
