{"_id":"72e976970dff4375","name":"Detox S Toxin","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"permanent","drain_code":"(F/2)-2]S","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!72e976970dff4375"}
{"_id":"d4f48da0c69f4096","name":"Diagnose","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"detection","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)-1]M","force":1,"description":"<p>The diagnose spell provides the spellcaster with information on any illnesses, injuries or other medical problems from which the subject suffers. To use the spell, the magician makes a Spell Success Test against a target number equal to 10 minus the subject's Essence Rating. For 1 success, the spell reveals whether the subject is healthy or ill and provides a general idea of the subject's Essence (high, average, dangerously low, hey-you're dead!). For 3 successes, the spell reveals specific illnesses or injuries, and for 5 successes it reveals even difficult-to-detect viruses (such as HMHVV) and internal injuries. This spell does not differentiate between low Essence due to deadly wounds or as a result of cyberware. The magician can only tell that something serious happened to the target's body.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!d4f48da0c69f4096"}
{"_id":"6a40d90ef9694cd7","name":"Displacement","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]S","force":1,"description":"<p>Illusion spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!6a40d90ef9694cd7"}
{"_id":"85633dff13c94d6d","name":"Disregard","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)M","force":1,"description":"<p>The disregard spell causes people to ignore a subject, though the subject remains visible. The spell can be defeated by a successful Intelligence Test.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!85633dff13c94d6d"}
{"_id":"b0311d32b2be4995","name":"Distant Invisibility","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Illusion spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!b0311d32b2be4995"}
{"_id":"a61d6635ac964472","name":"Dream","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)L","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell allows a magician to send a dream to a sleeping subject. The dream can't cause physical harm but can entertain, frighten, or relax the subject.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!a61d6635ac964472"}
