{"_id":"ad389a01f281460b","name":"Enhanced (Sense)","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"detection","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Detection spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!ad389a01f281460b"}
{"_id":"92d0bc19a5bc48fa","name":"Enhanced Sight","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"detection","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+4]D","force":1,"description":"<p>Detection spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!92d0bc19a5bc48fa"}
{"_id":"d722c0973ef74ee7","name":"Entertainment","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]L","force":1,"description":"<p>This area-effect spell requires voluntary subjects. It creates obvious, but entertaining, illusions for all who wish to watch. The number of successes measures how entertaining the audience finds the illusion.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!d722c0973ef74ee7"}
{"_id":"095b2db704684a4c","name":"Essence Drain","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]D","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!095b2db704684a4c"}
{"_id":"dfee1c1742ae4253","name":"Existential Blues","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!dfee1c1742ae4253"}
{"_id":"03ae2f8aae034e6f","name":"Extinguish Fire","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]S","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell can put out fires. The caster must make a successful Spell Success Test against the fire's Power Rating.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!03ae2f8aae034e6f"}
{"_id":"25fdec0e41504f40","name":"Fake Death","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Illusion spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!25fdec0e41504f40"}
{"_id":"1547edcc5ab14276","name":"False Memory","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"permanent","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]S","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell implants a false memory into a subject. The memory feels real, but the subject has a chance to realize it's false each time they recall it.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!1547edcc5ab14276"}
{"_id":"d4180db8c5a0436c","name":"Fashion","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"permanent","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell instantly tailors clothing, transforming the target's garments into any fashion the caster wishes. The fashion spell requires a voluntary subject. The caster's extrasuccesses measure the degree of style in the tailoring. Thespell cannot change the clothing's protective value, only its cut, color, and fit.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!d4180db8c5a0436c"}
{"_id":"ce20eb89cc6f400b","name":"Fast","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"permanent","drain_code":"(F/2)L","force":1,"description":"<p>The fast spell allows a voluntary subject to ignore hunger and thirst for 48 hours, though it does not replace the need for nourishment.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!ce20eb89cc6f400b"}
{"_id":"8f04043519954f11","name":"Fire Bolt","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"combat","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]D","force":1,"description":"<p>A powerful bolt of energy that causes Physical damage to a single target, using the elemental effect of fire.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!8f04043519954f11"}
{"_id":"abf95b088cac4f8f","name":"Fire Cloud","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"combat","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]D","force":1,"description":"<p>An area-effect cloud of magical energy that causes Physical damage, using the elemental effect of fire.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!abf95b088cac4f8f"}
{"_id":"d6f17e613f94429a","name":"Fire Dart","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"combat","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]M","force":1,"description":"<p>An energy dart that causes Physical damage to a single target, using the elemental effect of fire.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!d6f17e613f94429a"}
{"_id":"e48ac2ba63224d8e","name":"Fire Missle","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"combat","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]S","force":1,"description":"<p>A bolt of magical energy that causes Physical damage to a single target using the elemental effect of fire.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!e48ac2ba63224d8e"}
{"_id":"008872c859e14dc5","name":"Fire Strike","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+3]D","force":1,"description":"<p>This area-effect spell blasts flame into an area, using the elemental effect of fire.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!008872c859e14dc5"}
{"_id":"f12ce243031c4802","name":"Fireball","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"combat","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+3]D","force":1,"description":"<p>An area-effect spell that causes Physical damage. The fireball spell can ignite combustible materials in its blast area. Gamemaster discretion.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!f12ce243031c4802"}
{"_id":"d33dfdce7945423e","name":"FireFlies","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]D","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!d33dfdce7945423e"}
{"_id":"5527dd0b51c84d0c","name":"Firewall","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]D","force":1,"description":"<p>The firewall spell creates a wall of fire that causes damage to anything that touches it and provides visual cover. It does not block attacks but can detonate explosives.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!5527dd0b51c84d0c"}
{"_id":"ffb2accf6e714ee5","name":"Fix","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"permanent","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]M","force":1,"description":"<p>The fix spell repairs physical damage to inanimate objects. It cannot restore magical properties or bonds.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!ffb2accf6e714ee5"}
{"_id":"f672c2941d994d0c","name":"Flame Arrows","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"combat","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]D","force":1,"description":"<p>Combat spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!f672c2941d994d0c"}
{"_id":"3ab8b78523b2477d","name":"Flame Aura","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell creates a fiery aura around a subject that harms any attacker in melee combat. The flames do not harm the subject of the spell.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!3ab8b78523b2477d"}
{"_id":"150dc3b058dd497b","name":"Flame Barrier","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+3]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!150dc3b058dd497b"}
{"_id":"b4f938b3dbe943e0","name":"Flame Bomb","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]D","force":1,"description":"<p>This area-effect spell creates a blast whose effects surround the target. Being of real flame, it causes easily flammable materials to ignite and burn. The Damage Code for this attack is (F)M. Every 2 successes increases the damage by one level. The spell is resisted by Body, and one-half the value of Impact Armor reduces the Power (Force) of the attack. Resolve using the ranged combat procedure.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!b4f938b3dbe943e0"}
{"_id":"c915c449f86f4dd7","name":"Flame Burst","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]D","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell strikes the target with a burst of flame, using the elemental effect of fire.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!c915c449f86f4dd7"}
{"_id":"4ff7e4247c164e4e","name":"Flamethrower","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]S","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell creates a stream of flame from the caster to the target. Being of real flame, it causes easily flammable materials to ignite and burn. The Damage Code for this attack is (F)M. Every 2 successes increase the Damage Code by one level. The spell is resisted by Body. and one-half the value of Impact Armor reduces the Power (Force) of the attack. Resolve using the ranged combat procedure.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!4ff7e4247c164e4e"}
{"_id":"fdf947ce14ca4814","name":"Flare","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]M","force":1,"description":"<p>The flare spell creates a bright flash of light that can temporarily blind a target. The duration of the blindness depends on the caster's net successes.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!fdf947ce14ca4814"}
{"_id":"38eb01953170465d","name":"Flash","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Illusion spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!38eb01953170465d"}
{"_id":"e9ec3c9bfa6e4f6f","name":"Flight","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!e9ec3c9bfa6e4f6f"}
{"_id":"0197f2af4ae14c31","name":"Fling","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)M","force":1,"description":"<p>The fling spell hurls an object at a target with a force equal to the spell's Force. The object's weight is limited by the caster's Magic Attribute.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!0197f2af4ae14c31"}
