{"_id":"0b57352c2181482c","name":"Heal S Wounds","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"permanent","drain_code":"(F/2)-1]S","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!0b57352c2181482c"}
{"_id":"78d61c9cc7a84f00","name":"Heal","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"permanent","drain_code":"(F/2)(Wound Level)","force":1,"description":"<p>See Treat, above.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!78d61c9cc7a84f00"}
{"_id":"8f2d042eda974f39","name":"Healthy Glow","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"permanent","drain_code":"(F/2)L","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell brightens eyes and hair, sloughs off dead skin cells, improves circulation, and promotes general well-being. A cosmetic spell, the rich use the healthy glow spell as a status symbol and pick-me-up. Though \"permanent\" in the sense that it does not require magical sustaining, the spell will wear off in time, based on the subject's lifestyle, diet,vices, and so on.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!8f2d042eda974f39"}
{"_id":"e6999d59a6c641c5","name":"Heat Shield","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>The heat shield spell protects a target from fire and heat attacks. It reduces the Power of such attacks by the spell's Force Rating.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!e6999d59a6c641c5"}
{"_id":"9a628dd7bc5846e6","name":"Hellblast","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"combat","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+6]D","force":1,"description":"<p>An area-effect spell that causes Physical damage. The hellblast spell can ignite combustible materials in its blast area. Gamemaster discretion.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!9a628dd7bc5846e6"}
{"_id":"cf8d0dd236ca4b68","name":"Hibernate","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)S","force":1,"description":"<p>The magician must touch a voluntary or unconscious subject. The spell puts the subject in a form of suspended animation. Double the successes from the Spell Success Test to get the factor by which bodily processes are slowed. If 4 successes are scored, the hiber-nate spell slows the subject's metabolism by a factor of 8. If the subject has exceeded his Condition Monitor, he or she, or it would take an extra box of damage every 80 minutes instead of 10 minutes, as described in Exceeding the Condition Monitor, p. 111. If the subject were suffering from a disease that weakened him every hour, it would now take 8 hours. If he were sealed into a chamber with only enough air to keep him alive for 1 day, the air would now last 8 days.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!cf8d0dd236ca4b68"}
{"_id":"7bd3794f22a34442","name":"Hide Vehicle","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)M","force":1,"description":"<p>Illusion spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!7bd3794f22a34442"}
{"_id":"3b52468845ba4b2e","name":"Holograph","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"permanent","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]L","force":1,"description":"<p>Illusion spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!3b52468845ba4b2e"}
{"_id":"c1c177ac2f7643f8","name":"Ice Sheet","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]S","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell creates a flat sheet of ice that covers a number of square meters equal to the caster's Magic Rating multiplied by the successes. Characters crossing the sheet must make a Quickness Test against a Target Number 3 to avoid falling prone. Vehicles must make a Handling Test to avoid having to make a Crash Test. The sheet melts at a rate of 1 square meters per minute.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!c1c177ac2f7643f8"}
{"_id":"ae0b5547eb78417d","name":"Ignite","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"permanent","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]D","force":1,"description":"<p>The magician accelerates molecular speed in a target, making it catch fire. Anything that can burn is subject to this spell. The base time to ignite the target is 10 turns, divided by the magician's successes. Once the target ignites, it is burning until it either burns up or is extinguished by smothering, water, or a fire extinguisher. The spell must generated more successes than the Body Rating of living targets or the base Barrier Rating of inanimate objects. The ignite spell wraps a being in flames, causing (F)M damage on the first turn. The Power increases by 1 point per Combat Turn. At the end of each turn, make a Damage Resistance Test, counting one-half impact armor. Ammo or explosives carried by the victim may go off. If flames are not extinguished, they burn out in 1D6 Combat Turns.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!ae0b5547eb78417d"}
{"_id":"5ea142aabbd54bbc","name":"Illusionary Barrier","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]L","force":1,"description":"<p>Illusion spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!5ea142aabbd54bbc"}
{"_id":"81c2c2a1ef7d4d55","name":"Improved Invisibility","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Like the invisibility spell, below, except that this spell affects technological sensing devices.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!81c2c2a1ef7d4d55"}
{"_id":"966489e1e7594716","name":"Improved Mauler v1.2","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+4]D","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!966489e1e7594716"}
{"_id":"b031a57488074e8d","name":"Increase +1 Attribute","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]L","force":1,"description":"<p>The spell increases a normal Physical or Mental Attribute and Reaction (with special modifications) but not any other Special Attributes. The target number for the Spell Success Test is equal to twice the rating of the Attribute to be increased. A single success is sufficient. This spell does not affect cybernetic features, which require the spell described next. Each Attribute has four specific spells, and so there might be a magician who knows Increase Strength +2, Increase Quickness +1, and so on.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!b031a57488074e8d"}
{"_id":"ccc42f2431c34dce","name":"Increase +1 Cybered Attribute","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+3]L","force":1,"description":"<p>Like the increase attribute spell described above, except that these spells increase Attributes already affected by cybernetics. Increase cybered Reaction +4 has a [(F + 2) + 5]D code.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!ccc42f2431c34dce"}
