{"_id":"718f106263014648","name":"Increase Reflexes +1 die","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)M","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell increases the Initiative dice of the voluntary subject by the amount indicated for the spell (+1, +2, or +3). There is no cybered version of this spell, so characters who have received cybernetic enhancements that add Initiative dice (e.g., wired reflexes) cannot be boosted by this spell.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!718f106263014648"}
{"_id":"5e4b0c0123734965","name":"Increase Reflexes +2 dice","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)S","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!5e4b0c0123734965"}
{"_id":"6343555b260a4eb5","name":"Increase Reflexes +3 dice","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)D","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!6343555b260a4eb5"}
{"_id":"eed6aafa9b0243f2","name":"Inferno","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"combat","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)-1]D","force":1,"description":"<p>Combat spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!eed6aafa9b0243f2"}
{"_id":"99627e5d3c2f4962","name":"Influence","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"permanent","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]S","force":1,"description":"<p>Similar to the control thoughts spell (p. 157, SRII), this spell permanently implants a single suggestion in the victim's mind. He will act according to this suggestion or carry out this order as if it were his own idea. Proving the falseness of the idea to the victim, or forcing the caster to withdraw it, can overcome the spell.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!99627e5d3c2f4962"}
{"_id":"5921813c471142df","name":"Insect Barrier","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!5921813c471142df"}
{"_id":"52c326aec5cd47bb","name":"Intoxication","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell makes a subject feel drunk. The subject suffers Stun damage penalties to all actions based on the caster's successes. With 10 or more successes, the subject becomes incapacitated but remains conscious. This spell can be resisted by antidote or detox spells.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!52c326aec5cd47bb"}
{"_id":"196dc1f38282400e","name":"Invisibility","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)M","force":1,"description":"<p>The spellcaster must touch the subject, who becomes invisible to normal light. Thermographic vision can still detect body heat, and the subject is completely tangible and detectable to the senses of hearing, smell, and so forth. Double the number of successes to get the target number for an observer's Perception Test. A success-ful Perception Test means that the invisible person or thing has been noticed. The spell does not affect technological sensing systems (not including cybereyes which are considered natural because of the Essence Cost paid).</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!196dc1f38282400e"}
{"_id":"4b7799a09026438d","name":"Know Exit","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"detection","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+3]S","force":1,"description":"<p>Detection spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!4b7799a09026438d"}
{"_id":"eba321de87cc453c","name":"Levitate Item","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]L","force":1,"description":"<p>Levitation allows a magician to lift an item or person from the ground and move him or it around. The maximum \"distance\" that the target can be moved in meters is the magician's Magic Rating times the number of successes. This distance can be expressed as vertical distance (height), horizontal distance, or any combination of the two. A magician with a distance result of 12, for example, could move an object 12 meters horizontally, or 12 meters verti-cally or any combination of the two, as long as the total distance (horizontal plus vertical) equalled 12. This means that 10 horizontal and 2 vertical is fine (10 + 2 = 12), as is 5 horizontal and 7 vertical (5 + 7 = 12). The sum of the vertical and horizontal components must equal the \"distance.\" All movement is figured from the starting point of the target.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!eba321de87cc453c"}
{"_id":"13c286dc1cfc4335","name":"Levitate Person","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!13c286dc1cfc4335"}
{"_id":"d7e5f388cfe04df2","name":"Lift & Push","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)M","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!d7e5f388cfe04df2"}
{"_id":"edb8bdd4df0747fc","name":"Light Ray","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]D","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell fires a beam of light at a target with effects similar to a laser weapon.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!edb8bdd4df0747fc"}
{"_id":"1d6bea1523af441c","name":"Light","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>An area-effect spell. This spell creates a mobile point of light that illuminates an area equal to the magician's Magic Rating times the spell's successes in meters. The illumination is roughly equal to that from a good flashlight, but as an area-effect. This spell cannot be used to blind, but does offset visibility modifiers for darkness; 2 successes counters a +1 modifier.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!1d6bea1523af441c"}
{"_id":"5ffdaa092ba54ab1","name":"Lightning","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]S","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!5ffdaa092ba54ab1"}
{"_id":"c4aba3ede8b14e49","name":"Limited Fireball","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]D","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!c4aba3ede8b14e49"}
{"_id":"37f1c04639604bde","name":"Lock","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell holds any door, portal, closure, and other similar barriers magically closed as long as the caster sustains the spell. Because the lock has the same strength as the material of the door, opening it would require breaking or blasting through it.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!37f1c04639604bde"}
{"_id":"7e327d5c9e9f40a6","name":"Low-Light Vision","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"detection","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)L","force":1,"description":"<p>Detection spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!7e327d5c9e9f40a6"}
{"_id":"6e40ccde51aa4999","name":"Magesword II","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]S","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!6e40ccde51aa4999"}
{"_id":"be44583fa01e4bde","name":"Magesword","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]S","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!be44583fa01e4bde"}
{"_id":"c175618e7e3d42c4","name":"Magic Fingers","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Magic fingers is classic telekinesis. The magician creates \"invisible hands\" and can hold or manipulate items by mental power. The Spell Success Test has a Target Number 6. The number of successes becomes the spell's ratings for Strength and Quick-ness. The character can use his own skills with the magic fingers spell, but all target numbers receive a +2 because of the problems of remote control. Even simple actions may require a Quickness Test. The magician can fight, pick a lock, or whatever, using magic fingers. The fingers can reach any point the magician can see. The casting magician can use a clairvoyance spell or even remote-viewing technology to get a close-up of the scene, as long as the actual location is within his view. The spell comes in very handy for disarming bombs.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!c175618e7e3d42c4"}
{"_id":"804275780d484197","name":"Makeover","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"permanent","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell creates a complete makeover on a voluntary subject, including cosmetics, hair, clothes, and so on. It even polishes teeth and eliminates plaque. Changes wrought under this spell are as permanent as those made in a real beauty salon. The number of successes generated by the magician measures the degree of style in the makeover. Note that nothing actually changes; the subject is only cleaned and spruced up.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!804275780d484197"}
{"_id":"4c279106505d43a2","name":"Mana Barrier","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]S","force":1,"description":"<p>Mana barriers do not stop physical weapons, but they do block movement by living beings. Unliving things (like bullets) pass right through. Passengers inside closed vehicles are not affected by a mana barrier spell, but it would knock the rider off a motorcycle. A mana barrier spell also acts as a defense against spells. Add one-half the spell's Force (the barrier's Rating) to the target numbers of all magicians casting spells across the barrier. It is also an astral barrier.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!4c279106505d43a2"}
{"_id":"8ae38d460ba34621","name":"Mana Bolt","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"combat","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)S","force":1,"description":"<p>A powerful bolt of magical energy that causes Physical damage.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!8ae38d460ba34621"}
{"_id":"f58428641eff478d","name":"Mana Cloud","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"combat","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)S","force":1,"description":"<p>An area-effect spell that raises a cloud of magical energy that does Physical damage.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!f58428641eff478d"}
{"_id":"c807294fc4c84ef8","name":"Mana Dart","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"combat","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)L","force":1,"description":"<p>A small dart of magical power that does Physical damage.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!c807294fc4c84ef8"}
{"_id":"9a115aad68a0450d","name":"Mana Missile","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"combat","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)M","force":1,"description":"<p>A bolt of magical power that causes Physical damage.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!9a115aad68a0450d"}
{"_id":"5e4eadeb07a24e09","name":"Manaball","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"combat","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)S","force":1,"description":"<p>An area-effect spell that causes Physical damage. This mana version affects only living targets.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!5e4eadeb07a24e09"}
{"_id":"36fc01cc119a4b73","name":"Manablast","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"combat","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)D","force":1,"description":"<p>A powerful blast of magical energy that causes Physical damage. This area-effect spell uses the elemental effect of blast.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!36fc01cc119a4b73"}
{"_id":"aad5993134f04d8e","name":"Mask","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)L","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell requires that the magician touch a voluntary subject. The subject assumes some physical appearance (same basic size and shape) chosen by the caster. The number of successes becomes the target number for Perception Tests by observers. This spell does not work through technological devices.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!aad5993134f04d8e"}
{"_id":"a157a7f074ae4b3d","name":"Maya's Flame Burst","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]L","force":1,"description":"<p>Illusion spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!a157a7f074ae4b3d"}
{"_id":"6dd872fe44614810","name":"Memory Probe","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"detection","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+3]D","force":1,"description":"<p>Detection spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!6dd872fe44614810"}
{"_id":"3b548b0683e04dbe","name":"Mental Armor","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!3b548b0683e04dbe"}
{"_id":"b759f2a3565f4d3f","name":"Mental Shield","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]M","force":1,"description":"<p>The mental shield spell provides protection against spells and powers that affect the mind. It gives the target extra dice to resist such attacks.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!b759f2a3565f4d3f"}
{"_id":"74d030739b8b4814","name":"Mental Shields","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]L","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!74d030739b8b4814"}
{"_id":"e2827a2036014954","name":"Meteor Strike","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+6]D","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!e2827a2036014954"}
{"_id":"fa29b735f2f04968","name":"Mind Probe","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"detection","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]D","force":1,"description":"<p>The magician can telepathically probe a subject's mind. The target makes a Resistance Test using his Willpower Rating against a target number equal to the Force of the spell. If the target fails to offset all the successes, the number remaining determines the extent to which the magician can probe the target's mind. One success means that the magician can read surface thoughts. The magician knows what the target is thinking about at that instant, but cannot influence the thoughts or draw other information from the target. Two suc-cesses allow the magician to probe for thoughts. The magician can find out anything the subject knows consciously. He can ask any one question, and the target must answer with the truth as he knows it. Three or more successes allow the magician to enter the target's subconscious, and he can obtain the answer to two questions. Additional castings of this spell against the same target within a number of hours equal to the target's Willpower are at a +2 per attempt.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!fa29b735f2f04968"}
{"_id":"633b9c1e8305406c","name":"Mindlink (Individual)","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"detection","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>This is a hypersense spell requiring a voluntary subject that allows the casting magician to communicate mentally,exchanging conversation, emotions, and mental images with a specific person chosen at the time of the spell's design (presumably a teammate.). The subject must be within both line of sight and the range of the spell at the time of the initialcasting. Once the magician has cast the spell, the target must remain within the limited-range area, but may move out of line of sight. (Restricted Target: Individual).</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!633b9c1e8305406c"}
{"_id":"fd411a43f45b4f12","name":"Misinformation","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]S","force":1,"description":"<p>Illusion spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!fd411a43f45b4f12"}
{"_id":"5a142b9cab6e4521","name":"Mist","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]S","force":1,"description":"<p>This area-effect spell creates a dense mist that imposes vision penalties.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!5a142b9cab6e4521"}
{"_id":"0a554fcd0c61406f","name":"Mob Mind","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+3]S","force":1,"description":"<p>This area-effect spell allows the caster to control the thoughts of all within its range. For purposes of making aSuccess Test to gauge the spell's effect, treat the crowd as a single character. Pedestrians are assumed to have aWillpower of 3. Major characters, both player and non-player,should defend against the spell individually, based on the number of successes the caster generates with his or her single Force Success Test.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!0a554fcd0c61406f"}
{"_id":"88594e3a7d164da9","name":"Mob Mood","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Similar to the mob mind spell above, mob mood affects only the crowd's emotions. This spell does not give the caster control of a crowd, but allows him or her to shift a crowd's mood.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!88594e3a7d164da9"}
{"_id":"05643a69164c42c5","name":"Movement","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]S","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!05643a69164c42c5"}
{"_id":"a1fb5dce5b9845b3","name":"Net","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]D","force":1,"description":"<p>The net spell is a version of the bind spell that traps targets in an area of effect. Targets can resist with a Quickness Test. The magical net has a Barrier Rating equal to the caster's net successes.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!a1fb5dce5b9845b3"}
{"_id":"3c983c80644742ed","name":"Night Vision","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"detection","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)L","force":1,"description":"<p>The night vision spell grants the target the low-light vision modifiers listed on the Visibility Table, p. 89, SRII.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!3c983c80644742ed"}
{"_id":"75bea3db37cc484a","name":"Nutrition","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"permanent","drain_code":"(F/2)L","force":1,"description":"<p>The nutrition spell provides a full day's worth of nourishment and hydration to a voluntary subject using mana. It doesn't satisfy the feeling of hunger or thirst.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!75bea3db37cc484a"}
{"_id":"d565ae794c634661","name":"One-Way Barrier","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+3]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!d565ae794c634661"}
{"_id":"5cfd4ec1c6114f1c","name":"Overstimulation","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]M","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell stimulates the sensory centers of the target's brain. As long as the spell lasts, the subject suffers penalties to all actions as if a number of boxes equal to the caster's successes were filled in on the target's Stun condition monitor. The penalties do not reflect actual damage, but only represent the spell's effects. If the casting magician rolls 10 or more successes, the victim will be conscious but incapable of action.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!5cfd4ec1c6114f1c"}
{"_id":"80a6541d17b74018","name":"Oxygenate","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell, requiring a voluntary subject, oxygenates his or her blood, giving him or her extra Body dice (1 die for every 2 successes) to resist suffocation, strangulation, the effects of inhaled gas, or any other effect of oxygen deprivation. The spell also allows the subject to breathe water.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!80a6541d17b74018"}
{"_id":"24b3736be90f405f","name":"Paralyze","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]D","force":1,"description":"<p>The paralyze spell overrides a subject's voluntary muscles, making them unable to move or speak for the spell's duration. The subject can attempt a Willpower Test each round to break the spell.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!24b3736be90f405f"}
