{"_id":"b1a99bb77a3c4b96","name":"Resist Nuissance Allergy","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]L","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!b1a99bb77a3c4b96"}
{"_id":"eea455f43868481e","name":"Resist Pain L","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"permanent","drain_code":"(F/2)M","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell reduces the penalties suffered because ofPhysical damage (not Stun damage). Though this spell does not heal or treat damage, it offsets the injury modifiers (to the target number and Initiative) the character must use to reflect the damage. Magical assistance to resist pain requires a different spell for (L)ight, (M)oderate, and (S)erious Condition Levels. A resist pain spell cannot be used to counteract the pain of Deadly damage, because any character with a (D)eadly injury is unconscious and must be healed. The spell is \"permanent\" in that the boost to the patient's endorphin levels does not wear off. If the subject's damage rises above the Condition Level at which the patient is resisting pain, or the wounds heal, then the spell dissipates.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!eea455f43868481e"}
{"_id":"a4383075b75f46ab","name":"Resist Pain M","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"permanent","drain_code":"(F/2)S","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!a4383075b75f46ab"}
{"_id":"94ea2314f7bc4220","name":"Resist Paint S","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"permanent","drain_code":"(F/2)D","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!94ea2314f7bc4220"}
{"_id":"5e76eb07901d4254","name":"Resist Severe Allergy","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]D","force":1,"description":"<p>Health spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!5e76eb07901d4254"}
{"_id":"3ace1e614adc41c8","name":"Rot","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"combat","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]M","force":1,"description":"<p>The rot spell causes inanimate organic matter such as leather, wood, meat, paper and the like to decay rapidly and disintegrate. To cast the rot spell, the magician makes a Spell Test against an appropriate target number from the Object Resistance Table, p. 130, SRII. Note that the rot spell is effective against loa zombies, which are actually animated corpses. Against such zombies, the spell causes a base Damage Level of Serious. The target number is the zombie's Body Rating modified by any armor or magic. Because ghouls, vampires, banshees and other such undead are altered living creatures rather than dead beings, the rot spell does not affect them. This spell does not affect zombies created by zombie dust, or corps cadavres (see Zombies, p. 129).</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!3ace1e614adc41c8"}
{"_id":"f547d6fe8f564239","name":"Rubber Skin","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!f547d6fe8f564239"}
{"_id":"3d47e920e9c941ce","name":"Sap Strength","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]S","force":1,"description":"<p>The sap strength spell reduces a target's Strength Attribute. For every 2 successes, the target's Strength is reduced by 1. Against inanimate objects, it can cause them to collapse.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!3d47e920e9c941ce"}
{"_id":"66f2cb2a05d145d6","name":"Seal","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]S","force":1,"description":"<p>Similar to the lock spell listed above, this spell reinforces a locked doorway. Every 2 successes the caster generates increase the door's Barrier Rating by 1.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!66f2cb2a05d145d6"}
{"_id":"b856de4bdfa3413f","name":"Shadow","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>An area-effect spell. This spell creates a pool of darkness equal to one-half the caster's Magic Rating times the spell's successes in meters. The target number depends on the local conditions: bright midday, 6; day, 5; day, overcast, 4; twilight, 3; street light or darker, 2. Every 2 successes imposes a +1 target modifier for Combat or Perception Tests against targets within the area of shadow.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!b856de4bdfa3413f"}
{"_id":"0ab1ce98c67d4d28","name":"Shape Earth","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]D","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell allows the caster to magically move and shape a quantity of earth. It can be used to dig holes, fill trenches, or push over barricades.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!0ab1ce98c67d4d28"}
{"_id":"0aa1ad1824f34182","name":"Shape Water","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]D","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell works similarly to shape earth but affects water and other liquids.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!0aa1ad1824f34182"}
{"_id":"66297bc36b99481a","name":"Shapechange","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]S","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell transforms a voluntary subject into a normal critter, though the subject retains human consciousness. To determine the shapechanged critter's Physical Attributes,consult the Critter Statistics Table, p. 233, SRII, adding 1 to the critter's Base Ratings for every 2 successes the caster generates. Also, increase the critter's Reaction Rating by the subject's Intelligence Rating, to reflect the human mind controlling the animal form. Mental Attributes remain the subject's own. This spell does not transform clothing andequipment. Magicians under this spell can cast spells, but cannot fulfill geasa or use Centering Skills requiring activities that the animal shape cannot perform, such as speech.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!66297bc36b99481a"}
{"_id":"a19d1ba117dc4431","name":"Shattershield","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"combat","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)S","force":1,"description":"<p>The shattershield spell is specifically designed to break through magical barriers such as wards. The spell strikes the barrier with a single attack. If the attack is successful, reduce the Barrier or Ward Rating by 1, and for every 2 successes beyond the first, reduce the Barrier or Ward Rating by an additional 1 point. For example, 3 successes reduce the Ward Rating by 2, 5 successes reduce it by 3, and so on. Throretically, a character can shatter a ward with a single spell. To use the shattershield spell against astral barriers (such as wards or mana barriers), the spellcaster must be astrally active and able to assense the barrier when the spell is cast.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!a19d1ba117dc4431"}
{"_id":"bd617c52597f4bf0","name":"Silence","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]S","force":1,"description":"<p>This area-effect spell creates a sound-deadening field that prevents all sound from passing through or being created within it. It affects recording devices and sonic attacks.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!bd617c52597f4bf0"}
{"_id":"1d8cfd8cd39a4ee8","name":"Slay (Race/species)","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"combat","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)-1]S","force":1,"description":"<p>Each version of this spell has a different, specific formula. Slay ork, slay normal, slay dog, slay westerndragon, slay cockroach, slay feathered serpent, and so forth are all separate spells. (Restricted Target: Specific Race/Species)</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!1d8cfd8cd39a4ee8"}
{"_id":"a6b1589b194f4152","name":"Sleep","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"combat","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)-1]S","force":1,"description":"<p>An area-effect spell that causes Stun damage to living targets only.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!a6b1589b194f4152"}
{"_id":"5007771507d8410b","name":"Small Meteors","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]S","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!5007771507d8410b"}
{"_id":"35fceee4bceb4b2e","name":"Smoke Cloud","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+3]D","force":1,"description":"<p>This area-effect spell creates a cloud of smoke that inflicts Stun damage on targets within it and imposes a visibility penalty.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!35fceee4bceb4b2e"}
{"_id":"3840d58715a24044","name":"Sound Barrier","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]S","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!3840d58715a24044"}
{"_id":"0ef0817320164fea","name":"Sound Selection","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"detection","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)L","force":1,"description":"<p>Detection spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!0ef0817320164fea"}
{"_id":"949a8a955edc4032","name":"Spark","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]M","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell creates a small spark of electricity that springs from the spellcaster to the target. The damage code for this attack is (F)M. Every 2 successes increase the Damage Code by one level. The spell is resisted by Body, and one-half the value of Impact Armor reduces the Power (Force) of the attack. Resolve using the ranged combat procedure.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!949a8a955edc4032"}
{"_id":"451469f6968d42f7","name":"Spectacle","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]M","force":1,"description":"<p>A multi-sensory version of the entertainment spell (p.156, SRII.).</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!451469f6968d42f7"}
{"_id":"5c1a38b4e3de4140","name":"Spell Barrier","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Similar to the mana barrier spell (p. 158, SRII), the spellbarrier spell provides protection against spells. The personal form of this spell has a Drain Code of [(F / 2)+2]L.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!5c1a38b4e3de4140"}
{"_id":"3c98fc756de64265","name":"Spirit Barrier","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell creates a barrier that only affects spirits and other astral entities. It does not block dual-natured creatures or magical items.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!3c98fc756de64265"}
{"_id":"130ecd08cb664091","name":"Spirit Bolt","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"combat","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)-1]S","force":1,"description":"<p>A bolt of magical energy that causes Physical damage to a single spirit. (Restricted Target: Spirits.)</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!130ecd08cb664091"}
{"_id":"5653eb020f604b8b","name":"Stabilize","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"health","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"permanent","drain_code":"(F/2)S","force":1,"description":"<p>When applied to a character with Deadly Physical damage, this spell stabilizes his condition so that he does not die. The magician must add the number of minutes elapsed since the character took damage to his or her target number for the Spell Success Test.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!5653eb020f604b8b"}
{"_id":"c23ce81e05704586","name":"Steel Skin","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]S","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!c23ce81e05704586"}
{"_id":"e4786a5a963548f6","name":"Sterilize","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"combat","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]D","force":1,"description":"<p>This area-effect spell kills small life forms such as bacteria and other microorganisms. In addition, it also destroys or renders unusable such biomaterial as skinflakes, stray hairs, spilled blood, and so forth that might be left behind at a crime scene. Organic material affected by this spell cannot be used as a material link (see RitualMagic, p. 35, and p. 135, SRII). Because the spell does not affect biomaterial attached to a living being, it does not kill the various helpful and harmful microorganisms living inside a creature. Successful application of the spell requires only 1 success. For game purposes, this spell does not affect organisms classified as bioweapons.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!e4786a5a963548f6"}
{"_id":"946505fd3d0a4e97","name":"Stimulation","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]L","force":1,"description":"<p>The voluntary subject experiences a full sensory illusion of whatever type the spellcaster desires. This is usually a luxury spell bought by the rich and jaded, seeking sensations they cannot find in the real world. Successes measure the pleasure of the subject.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!946505fd3d0a4e97"}
{"_id":"d19d57cd54914182","name":"Stink","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"illusion","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]S","force":1,"description":"<p>This area spell stimulates the sense of smell. Subjects within the area of effect make normal Spell Resistance Tests to reduce the magician's successes. Each remaining success increases all of the victims' target numbers by +1 because of the sickening effect of the smell's stench.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!d19d57cd54914182"}
{"_id":"64eaa013c73d43a3","name":"Stoplight Control","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]L","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!64eaa013c73d43a3"}
{"_id":"9c050552751e47b4","name":"Stun Bolt","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"combat","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)-1]D","force":1,"description":"<p>A bolt of magical energy that causes Stun damage to a single target.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!9c050552751e47b4"}
{"_id":"67bb52e84b594dbc","name":"Stun Cloud","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"combat","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)-1]S","force":1,"description":"<p>An area-effect spell, instantly producing a cloud of magical energy that causes Stun damage.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!67bb52e84b594dbc"}
{"_id":"01a99d144b9b4244","name":"Stun Missile","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"combat","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)-1]M","force":1,"description":"<p>A missile of magical energy that causes Stun damage to a single target.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!01a99d144b9b4244"}
{"_id":"d3aa54fc8754421c","name":"Stun Touch","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"combat","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)-2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>A hands-on spell that causes Stun damage to a single target.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!d3aa54fc8754421c"}
{"_id":"44a52dd6f0004e5b","name":"Stunball","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"combat","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)-1]D","force":1,"description":"<p>An area-effect spell that causes Stun damage to a single target.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!44a52dd6f0004e5b"}
{"_id":"fb3a9e7fd82149f5","name":"Stunblast","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"combat","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]D","force":1,"description":"<p>An area-effect spell that causes Stun damage using the elemental effect of blast.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!fb3a9e7fd82149f5"}
