{"_id":"65556aea5b9c45e4","name":"Terrorize","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"mana","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]S","force":1,"description":"<p>The terrorize spell fills a target with overwhelming fear of the caster, causing them to flee. The subject can make a Willpower Test each round to overcome the effect.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!65556aea5b9c45e4"}
