{"_id":"cc4e3327bc814c62","name":"Wind","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)+1]S","force":1,"description":"<p>The wind spell creates a powerful gust of wind that can knock over objects and living targets.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!cc4e3327bc814c62"}
{"_id":"bc36bb4a2d914ff0","name":"Wrecker","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"combat","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"instant","drain_code":"(F/2)S","force":1,"description":"<p>This spell works in a manner similar to the ram spell (p.151, SRII), but affects only a single vehicle. (RestrictedTarget: Vehicles.)</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!bc36bb4a2d914ff0"}
{"_id":"b67e5160f9974eff","name":"X-Ray Specs","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"manipulation","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]M","force":1,"description":"<p>Manipulation spell. Description will be populated from RAG database.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!b67e5160f9974eff"}
{"_id":"5a9f1f4230da4607","name":"X-Ray Vision","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-purple.webp","system":{"category":"detection","type":"physical","range":"los","duration":"sustained","drain_code":"(F/2)+2]S","force":1,"description":"<p>The x-ray vision spell enables a willing subject to see through inanimate barriers. For each success on the spellcaster's Spell Success Test, the subject can see through 1 Barrier Rating Point of non-living objects. The subject must spend a Simple Action to do so. The line of sight provided by the x-ray vision spell fulfills the LOS requirement for casting other spells. The x-ray vision spell does not enable subjects to see through living or magical barriers, and does not work in astral space.</p>"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"},"_key":"!items!5a9f1f4230da4607"}
